Shillbot confirmed on 4chan. Further investigation revealed an entire network.

Confirmation of automated shitposting 12-27-13
On the night of December 27, a bot went apeshit on 4chan, posting so much shit it seemed hard to find a legit thread. Almost all of these threads/images/premises/copypasta had been seen for months but never in such volume. Someone started a thread calling it out.
